  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK790">
<l>iṉaiya rivarnamak kiṉṉamyā meṉṟu</l>
<l>puṉaiyiṉum pulleṉṟu naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though friends may praise one another saying, "He is so intimate with us, and we so much (with him)"; (still) such friendship will appear mean.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
